# Closing thoughts

Text, images, and embeddings are the raw material of modern AI applications, and none of them fit neatly into a relational schema. **NoSQL for unstructured data** handles all three naturally, keeping related context together, adapting to structural changes without migrations, and scaling with the pipeline as AI workloads grow. For teams building serious AI products, getting the data layer right from the start is one of the highest-leverage decisions they can make.
